00:19:42,048 --> 00:19:43,144
One more time and we're almost done.

291
00:19:43,552 --> 00:19:45,544
Yuning, just toss in the rice
and stir-fry.

292
00:19:45,632 --> 00:19:46,272
Okay.

293
00:19:46,272 --> 00:19:46,912
Then it won't splatter.

294
00:19:46,912 --> 00:19:48,104
Just stir-fry everything all in one pot.

295
00:19:48,192 --> 00:19:49,472
Yes.

296
00:19:50,208 --> 00:19:52,384
Just send someone
to cover every microphone.

297
00:19:54,016 --> 00:19:55,424
Why don't you just put it in your mouth?

298
00:19:57,568 --> 00:19:58,400
Low-temperature oil.

299
00:19:58,400 --> 00:19:59,424
Yuning, do you have any experience?

300
00:19:59,648 --> 00:20:00,544
No.

301
00:20:05,792 --> 00:20:07,064
Second round failed.

302
00:20:07,064 --> 00:20:07,776
The punishment is

303
00:20:07,776 --> 00:20:09,344
for everyone to eat

304
00:20:09,568 --> 00:20:10,864
one grape at the table.

305
00:20:12,864 --> 00:20:14,264
Let's cheer ourselves on.

306
00:20:14,688 --> 00:20:16,704
- Wow The World!
- Wow The World!

307
00:20:16,736 --> 00:20:19,168
- The whole world is right here!
- The whole world is right here!

308
00:20:26,272 --> 00:20:27,344
Eat the grapes first.

309
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:28,800
Just this one.

310
00:20:30,184 --> 00:20:31,520
It's so sour it's killing me!

311
00:20:31,520 --> 00:20:33,544
My teeth are tingling.

312
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:34,624
Just one.

313
00:20:34,624 --> 00:20:35,424
Very sour.

314
00:20:49,088 --> 00:20:50,752
Lin Yi swallowed it.

315
00:21:00,032 --> 00:21:00,864
So sour.

316
00:21:08,184 --> 00:21:10,624
Xingxu and Lin Yi are truly
two strange people.

317
00:21:10,624 --> 00:21:12,512
Weird way of thinking.

318
00:21:28,184 --> 00:21:30,080
Jingfei, this is way too messy.

319
00:21:30,344 --> 00:21:32,224
- It's fine. This is for us anyway.
- This is too messy.

320
00:21:36,104 --> 00:21:36,992
Too much.

321
00:21:51,864 --> 00:21:53,024
Let it soak for a while.

322
00:21:56,448 --> 00:21:57,304
Let it soak for a while.

323
00:22:06,560 --> 00:22:07,864
Help me turn on the water.

324
00:22:08,448 --> 00:22:09,728
Give me a little bit of water.

325
00:22:09,728 --> 00:22:11,704
- Just a little bit of water.
- No water allowed.

326
00:22:13,944 --> 00:22:14,544
But my hand

327
00:22:14,544 --> 00:22:15,584
is too sticky.

328
00:22:15,968 --> 00:22:16,824
Bear with it.

329
00:22:18,656 --> 00:22:19,648
Just eat it.

330
00:22:19,840 --> 00:22:20,832
Like this.

331
00:22:21,824 --> 00:22:22,400
Wipe it.

332
00:22:39,040 --> 00:22:39,520
Light soy sauce.

333
00:22:44,672 --> 00:22:45,312
Later,

334
00:22:45,312 --> 00:22:46,144
try tearing it with one hand.

335
00:22:52,352 --> 00:22:53,384
Lin Yi

336
00:22:53,384 --> 00:22:54,824
was like a snake.

337
00:22:56,576 --> 00:22:57,088
It's prickly.

338
00:22:57,088 --> 00:22:57,944
Did you get pricked?

339
00:23:11,544 --> 00:23:12,160
That's enough.

340
00:23:18,048 --> 00:23:19,184
There's even a ring?

341
00:23:27,024 --> 00:23:28,384
Let me do it.

342
00:23:30,104 --> 00:23:31,464
What expression is this?

343
00:23:40,344 --> 00:23:40,944
Hurry up.

344
00:23:40,944 --> 00:23:43,144
Flip it quickly. It's about to burn.

345
00:23:43,144 --> 00:23:44,584
Pour it in.

346
00:24:00,192 --> 00:24:01,664
This looks like rice porridge.

347
00:24:07,104 --> 00:24:09,344
How on earth did we eat this back then?

348
00:24:09,624 --> 00:24:10,944
I remember it tasted pretty tasty.

349
00:24:10,944 --> 00:24:11,544
It's okay to eat.

350
00:24:11,544 --> 00:24:12,904
Just a bit greasy.

351
00:24:12,904 --> 00:24:14,584
Didn't he see rubbing your hands?

352
00:24:15,520 --> 00:24:17,064
Stir-frying it like this
actually tastes pretty good.

353
00:24:20,736 --> 00:24:21,280
Done.

354
00:24:21,280 --> 00:24:21,952
Done.

355
00:24:22,336 --> 00:24:23,008
Slowly.

356
00:24:28,128 --> 00:24:29,056
It's ready to eat.

357
00:24:31,040 --> 00:24:32,032
Come on. Give me a bite.

358
00:24:32,032 --> 00:24:32,864
I'll taste it first.

359
00:24:44,960 --> 00:24:45,824
It's ready to eat.

360
00:24:45,824 --> 00:24:46,528
No problem with that.

361
00:24:46,528 --> 00:24:47,104
Go ahead and eat.

362
00:24:47,104 --> 00:24:48,224
Come on. One bite each.

363
00:24:50,336 --> 00:24:52,064
The point is we're using
the same spatula.

364
00:24:52,832 --> 00:24:53,471
Is it good?

365
00:24:54,344 --> 00:24:55,304
Not bad.

366
00:24:55,304 --> 00:24:55,784
Let me try it.

367
00:24:57,280 --> 00:24:57,824
Hot.

368
00:24:58,464 --> 00:24:59,224
Too hot.

369
00:24:59,840 --> 00:25:00,464
Good.

370
00:25:00,960 --> 00:25:01,664
Okay.

371
00:25:07,200 --> 00:25:07,984
Good.

372
00:25:08,480 --> 00:25:09,264
It's not bad, right?

373
00:25:09,264 --> 00:25:10,064
Really tasty.

374
00:25:11,636 --> 00:25:12,500
Let me have a bite.

375
00:25:13,184 --> 00:25:14,016
A little bit hot.

376
00:25:14,784 --> 00:25:15,200
A little less.

377
00:25:15,200 --> 00:25:16,024
Take a smaller bite.

378
00:25:17,056 --> 00:25:17,856
Is it good?

379
00:25:18,272 --> 00:25:18,984
Not bad.

380
00:25:18,984 --> 00:25:20,256
- It's good.
- Not bad.

381
00:25:43,584 --> 00:25:44,264
Not bad, right?

382
00:25:44,928 --> 00:25:47,264
There's a rice grain
stuck in my throat right now.

383
00:25:48,384 --> 00:25:49,120
Don't laugh.

384
00:25:49,120 --> 00:25:50,104
Bear with it.

385
00:25:50,528 --> 00:25:51,384
Stop talking.

386
00:25:54,080 --> 00:25:54,584
Hot.

387
00:26:01,728 --> 00:26:02,504
Perfect.

388
00:26:03,808 --> 00:26:05,544
Should we dish it out?

389
00:26:08,128 --> 00:26:08,624
Okay.

390
00:26:08,624 --> 00:26:09,304
That's enough.

391
00:26:09,304 --> 00:26:09,864
Okay.

392
00:26:13,056 --> 00:26:14,424
There are two pairs of chopsticks
unexpectedly.

393
00:26:14,424 --> 00:26:16,664
Were you rubbing your hands
inside that bowl the whole time?

394
00:26:16,664 --> 00:26:18,400
I actually didn't rub my hands
inside the bowl.

395
00:26:18,720 --> 00:26:19,424
I've completely forgotten.

396
00:26:23,584 --> 00:26:25,472
Challenge successful.

397
00:26:26,144 --> 00:26:27,040
Let's go eat.

398
00:26:27,328 --> 00:26:27,840
Let's go.
